        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "11. I will rebuke—(See on [1195]Mal 2:3). I will no longer \"rebuke (English Version, 'corrupt') the seed,\" but will rebuke every agency that could hurt it (Am 4:9).",
        "children": []
      }
    ]
  },
