        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". \"Bring ye all the tithe into the treasure-house, that there may be consumption in my house, and prove me now herewith, saith Jehovah of hosts, if I do not open you the sluices of heaven, and pour you out a blessing to superabundance. ",
