        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Malachi 3:10",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " the emphasis lies upon kol: the whole of the tithe they are to bring, and not merely a portion of it, and so defraud the Lord; for the tithe was paid to Jehovah for His servants the Levites (",
