      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Numbers 18:24",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "). It was delivered, at least after the times of the later kings, at the sanctuary, where store-chambers were built for the purpose (cf. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "2 Chronicles 31:11",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
